text: Bjørn Inge Mo (16 March 1968 – 10 July 2022) was a Norwegian politician. He was a member of the Labour Party. He was mayor of Kåfjord from 2003 to 2015. He was in the Sámi Parliament of Norway from 2017 to 2020. Mo died on 10 July 2022 at the age of 54. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:2022 deaths Category:Norwegian mayors
